  <answer><![CDATA[<p><span>A payment will be required at the end of the booking process. If you are booking a holiday more than 10 weeks prior to travel, you will only pay a deposit of £150 per person to confirm the booking while the full balance will be due 10 weeks before departure. If you are booking within 10 weeks of your holiday departure date, full payment is required at the time of booking.</span></p>]]></answer>
